QuestData.Title: Favor: Pristine Dredbat Fang
QuestData.Description:
This item will be of great interest to the brokers.
Per your previous deal with The Night Market, you should bring it to Ta'xera.
You will be fairly compensated.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Pristine Dredbat Fang to Ta'xera at The Night Market in Revendreth.
